{"id":606837,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【立此存照】绵阳网警开始在twitter执法了？/","date":"2019-03-03T03:33:26Z","modified":"2019-03-03T03:33:26Z","title":"【立此存照】“绵阳网警”开始在twitter执法了？","content":"<p>近日，有网友发现，一个注册信息是“绵阳网警巡查执法”的twitter账号 @mywjxczf 宣称已在twitter上进行执法。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">我们开始在推特上进行执法了</p>\n<p>&mdash; 绵阳网警巡查执法 (@mywjxczf) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mywjxczf/status/1099940510859444224?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 25, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">目前该推文收到不少谴责回应</p>\n<p>该账号开通于2018年9月，截至目前仅发布推文12条，其中5条都是网民发言遭落地抓捕的新闻通报。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-2' class='gallery galleryid-606837 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e7%bd%91%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b%e5%9c%a8twitter%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f/%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e7%bd%91%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b%e5%9c%a8twitter%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f/%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%952/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法2-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法2-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法2-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法2-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e7%bd%91%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b%e5%9c%a8twitter%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f/%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%953/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法3-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法3-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法3-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法3-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e7%bd%91%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b%e5%9c%a8twitter%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f/%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%954/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法4-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法4-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法4-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法4-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e7%bd%91%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b%e5%9c%a8twitter%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f/%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%955/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法5-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法5-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法5-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法5-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl>\n\t\t\t<br style='clear: both' />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>目前暂不清楚，该账号是否是绵阳网警真实持有的账号。但 @绵阳网警巡查执法 目前在新浪微博有<a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/1010712057\">同名账号</a>，微博认证信息为“绵阳市公安局网络安全保卫支队”，并且同一天在新浪和twitter有发布一致的内容。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606846\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法6.png 737w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法6-300x223.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606847\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"531\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法7.png 730w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/绵阳执法7-300x290.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>此前，四川绵阳市并不乏“敢为人先”的举动，例如在2019年1月1日起，绵阳市交警支队就已经开始实行“带枪巡逻”，给部分交警配备92G手枪，授予其对治安、刑事案件的先期处置权限。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB-%E8%8D%B7%E6%9E%AA%E5%AE%9E%E5%BC%B9%EF%BC%81%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E7%BB%B5%E9%98%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A61%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7/\">封面新闻 | 荷枪实弹！四川绵阳城区部分交警1日起带枪巡逻</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/bbc-%e5%9b%9b%e5%b7%9d%e7%bb%b5%e9%98%b3%e5%85%ac%e5%ae%89%e5%b1%80%e5%89%af%e5%b1%80%e9%95%bf%e8%a2%ab%e8%b0%83%e6%9f%a5/\">BBC | 四川绵阳公安局副局长被调查</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1019,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9249,9503,9212,15025]}